Pre-Game Insights: Australia, despite the win against Sri Lanka in their previous game, are sixth on the points table. Every match in the group stage has assumed importance as the Aussies cannot afford losses anymore.
Pakistan, meanwhile, are fourth on the points table, with the clash against Australia a chance to put behind the memory of a harrowing loss last time out.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match between Australia and Pakistan will be played at the M. Chinnaswamy Stadium in Bangalore.
The live streaming of the game between Australia and Pakistan will be on Disney+ Hotstar.
Others: The ICC World Cup 2023 game between Australia and Pakistan will be played on Friday, October 20, 2023.
The game between Australia and Pakistan is scheduled to kickstart at 14:00 (IST) (+5:30 GMT).
